attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Gary Greene -

data.description: Gorgeous Mediterranean-style townhome just off NASA Blvd, close to NASA, Clear Lake, and Kemah! First floor features a spacious secondary bedroom and en-suite bath, perfect for guests, MIL, or home office. Main floor living on the 2nd floor showcases beautiful wood floors throughout. Bright and airy living room has loads of natural light. Enjoy an arched entry to the second seating area in the open-concept kitchen with large island with seating, granite counters, SS appliances, breakfast room, and balcony access. Head to the 3rd floor for an incredible owner's suite! Spacious bedroom connects to the breathtaking bathroom with a coffee bar, dual vanities, soaking tub, walk-in shower, and enormous walk-in closet with built-ins! Laundry room on 3rd floor for added convenience. Don't miss the incredible pond views from multiple balconies, including rooftop. Fridge and washer/dryer stay. Enjoy the community pool with pond view or take a short drive to the Kemah Boardwalk for entertainment!
